sraeli-Hamas war\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"Xi\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"this conflict\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"quite some time\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said it is a \\\"tragedy\\\" that is \\\"a test of the human conscience.\\\"\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"tragedy\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a test\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"the human conscience\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The international community must do something.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The international community\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We call for an immediate, comprehensive and sustainable cease-fire in Gaza,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999504467484563, \"rank\": 4.955570708901515e-05, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an immediate, comprehensive and sustainable cease-fire\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xi said China also supports Palestine becoming a member of the UN.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.999972174277598, \"rank\": 2.5778532696814952e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinian_territories\", \"score\": 0.8383516737676402,